In the process of contrasting this translation with the status quo, I've uncovered a latent bug.

{code}
class C {
  def catchExpr1: PartialFunction[Throwable, Any] = ???
  def test = {
    try {} catch catchExpr1
  }
}
{code}

{noformat}
